parameters:
The gaze of a tall man who came out of the
elevator falls on my chest.

To reprimand \r[ for their overly brazen gaze, I
glared at the man.
\n<A man wearing a cardigan>Director Udo! We've been waiting for you!

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (I can't just throw it away...
Seriously, what should I do about this...)

\n<Male Janitor>Ah, sorry! I just waxed the floor and it's
slippery, so please use the elevator \C[2] for
your own safety!

\n<\N[5]>Hey, Minato Neon... could you please cheer up and
have some shisomeru tea?

\n<Minato Neon>Hey, don't just naturally make me try out new
products! It's true that I was a little curious
about this, but...

\n<\N[5]>More importantly... what's really going on? Even
though it's just a meeting, you haven't been able
to concentrate the whole time, right?

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F] I'm telling you, it's
nothing... Nn... Ugh... What is this? It's so
sweet...

The man standing in front of me tightens the
bottle cap he's holding in his hand and screws the
main body into the pocket of his jacket.

\n<\N[5]>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF] .........Since today I
only have to show up at the office, how about we
go on a short tour to take our minds off things? I
have a company car, but...
\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F] ......Not bad.

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F] Ah... I just had a little
thought.

\n<\N[5]>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF]I didn't think so. Come on,
let's go.

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F] Hey, don't casually reject
the Sisomeron tea!

\n<Excited Senior AD>I just greeted Minato Neon-sama earlier! She was,
like... super sexy and cool! N-not that I'm
looking at her like that or anything! I totally
respect her as an artist! Oh, by the way, I
actually went to her concert the other day, you
know...

\n<Socially dying junior AD>(Grrr... I really need to go to the bathroom!!
This person just talks and talks forever!!)

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (There are also chestnut soda and tartar
juice, among others. It's quite a challenging
lineup.)

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (...It's just an ordinary fire
extinguisher.)

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (It's an information board made of
transparent glass. It seems that there are several
discussion rooms on this floor, as well as the
second and third studios.)
\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (It's a well-maintained potted plant)

\n<A passionate man's voice>\F[\V[2]] Based on all of this... I will prove the
usefulness of the creamy red bean juice! Please
consider changing the lineup of vending
machines...
\n<The voice of a man who cuts ruthlessly>\F[\V[2]] ...No, that's red bean soup, right?
\n<Angry man's voice>\F[\V[2]] What the hell? Who the hell are you...?

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]] (It seems like a pointless debate is
heating up...)

\n<Minato Neon>This is the conference room where we were having a
meeting until just now. We don't need it anymore.

\n<\N[5]>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF] I've been thinking about
this every year... Isn't that outfit hot during
the summer?

\n<Minato Neon>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F] It's a custom-made outfit
for summer, so it's not as hot as you think.
